Searching.description:
Inspired by some of today's biggest EDM tracks, Throttle has taken bits and pieces from 20 different tracks, combining them live on a launchpad to create his mashup titled 'Inspire'

Watch the video: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TZAf_tuu-6M

Follow Monstercat:
Facebook: http://facebook.com/MonstercatMedia
Twitter: http://twitter.com/MonstercatMedia
Soundcloud: http://soundcloud.com/Monstercat

Follow Throttle:
Facebook:https://facebook.com/throttleofficial
Soundcloud:http://soundcloud.com/throttle
Youtube:http://youtube.com/officialthrottle

Mashup Tracklist:
Aloe Blacc - I Need a Dollar
AN21 & Max Vangeli vs. Steve Angello - H8RS
Axwell feat. Errol Reid - Nothing But Love
Breakbot - Fantasy
Dada Life - Kick Out The Epic Motherf**ker
Daft Punk - Harder Better Faster Stronger
Deadmau5 - Raise Your Weapon (Madeon Remix)
Felguk - All Night Long (Darth and Vader Mix)
Frankmusik - Confusion Girl (Russ Chimes Remix)
Frida Gold - Zeig Mir Wie Du Tanzt (Skrillex Remix)
Knife Party - Rage Valley (Original Mix)
Madeon - Icarus
Martin Solveig - The Night Out (Madeon Remix)
Miami Horror - Moon Theory (Sam La More Remix)
Miike Snow - A Horse is Not a Home
Outkast - Roses
Porter Robinson - Unison (Knife Party Remix)
Sheff - The Kitchen (Darth & Vader Remix)

Searching.title: Inspire
